desc_short	-----								The first and only official Rube Goldberg puzzle game. Solve everyday problems in Rube’s trademark elaborate style by creating complex and hilarious machines. Is pouring a glass of juice just too straightforward and boring? Try using a jack-in-the-box, magnifying glass, string and a cymbal-wielding friend to achieve your goal.							
developer									Electric Eggplant					,			Kalani Games, Inc.					,			HRG (Heirs of Rube Goldberg)					,			Unity Games								
